Install the libraries(SpaCy – scispaCy – ‘en_core_sci_sm’/’en_ner_bc5cdr_md’).
We can install these libraries by using pip install https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/ai2-s2-scispacy/releases/v0.5.4/en_core_sci_sm-0.5.4.tar.gz this command.
Install the libraries (Transformers (Hugging Face) - and any bio-medical model (BioBert) that can detect drugs, diseases, etc from the text). 
We can intstall these libraris by unsing pip install transformers.
